HOW TO DIRECTLY FIND A DESCRIPTION OF A VIRUS.


    When you have started VIB either from the CLI or Workbench you are
    presented  with  the  main screen.  The top 28 gadgets represent a
    directory  where  the descriptions of the vira lies.  Lets say you
    want  information  on the virus 'Northstar'.  You would then press
    the gadget with the letter 'N' in it or as a shortcut press 'n' on
    your  keyboard.  You will now see a list of the directory 'N' with
    the names of the vira which starts with an 'N' (basic enough).

@endnode

